commits.author: Steven Rowe
commits.sourceNew:
/** * For a document containing all the phrase query terms, compute the * frequency of the phrase in that document. * A non zero frequency means a match. *
Note, that containing all phrase terms does not guarantee a match - they have to be found in matching locations. * @return frequency of the phrase in current doc, 0 if not found. */ abstract float phraseFreq() throws IOException;
